edu.ucla.sspace.tools
Class PsudoWordSelector

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.tools.PsudoWordSelector

public class PsudoWordSelector
extends Object

A utility for selecting a set of pseudo words. It takes in a list of words and their scores, and optionally a list of words that should serve as the basis for any psuedoword. The output will be a list of mappings from the original term to it's pseudo word. This also supports separation by parts of speech. When using parts of speech, confounders will always have the same part of speech.

Author:
Keith Stevens
